你现在这个服务器串虽然已经把内层 `?l=zh-Hans-CN` 编成了 `%3Fl%3Dzh-Hans-CN`，**但客户端在 `/Users/liuyifu/Documents/oversea/AppHub/WhatsBox/WhatsBox/Core/Service/Routing/WBRouteExpress.m:11` 先把整串 query 全量解码了**，然后父类再按 `=` 拆参数，结果又把内层 URL 里的 `=` 当成外层分隔符，所以还是会在你贴的断言那里炸。

**你要改的点**
- 文件：`/Users/liuyifu/Documents/oversea/AppHub/WhatsBox/WhatsBox/Core/Service/Routing/WBRouteExpress.m:11`
- 不要再：
  - 先整串 `URLDecode`
  - 再 `super parseQueryString`
- 要改成：
  - 先按原始 query 的 `&` 拆 entry
  - 每个 entry 单独解码
  - 每个 entry 只按**第一个** `=` 分成 key/value

**直接替换成这个**
```objc
//
//  WBRouteExpress.m
//  WhatsBox
//

#import "WBRouteExpress.h"

@implementation WBRouteExpress

- (NSDictionary *)parseQueryString:(NSString *)queryString {
    if (queryString.length == 0) {
        return nil;
    }

    NSArray<NSString *> *entries = [queryString componentsSeparatedByString:@"&"];
    NSMutableDictionary *result = [NSMutableDictionary dictionaryWithCapacity:entries.count];

    for (NSString *entry in entries) {
        if (entry.length == 0) {
            continue;
        }

        NSString *decodedEntry = [entry stringByRemovingPercentEncoding] ?: entry;
        NSRange separatorRange = [decodedEntry rangeOfString:@"="];
        if (separatorRange.location == NSNotFound) {
            continue;
        }

        NSString *key = [decodedEntry substringToIndex:separatorRange.location];
        NSString *valueString = [decodedEntry substringFromIndex:separatorRange.location + separatorRange.length];

        if (key.length == 0) {
            continue;
        }

        NSString *finalValueString = [self wb_stringByRemovingWrappedQuotes:valueString];
        id finalValue = [self wb_inferredValueFromString:finalValueString];
        result[key] = finalValue ?: @"";
    }

    return result.copy;
}

- (NSString *)wb_stringByRemovingWrappedQuotes:(NSString *)string {
    if (string.length < 2) {
        return string ?: @"";
    }

    unichar first = [string characterAtIndex:0];
    unichar last = [string characterAtIndex:string.length - 1];
    BOOL singleQuoted = (first == '\'' && last == '\'');
    BOOL doubleQuoted = (first == '"' && last == '"');

    if (singleQuoted || doubleQuoted) {
        return [string substringWithRange:NSMakeRange(1, string.length - 2)];
    }

    return string;
}

- (id)wb_inferredValueFromString:(NSString *)string {
    if (string.length == 0) {
        return @"";
    }

    NSString *lowercased = string.lowercaseString;
    if ([lowercased isEqualToString:@"true"]) {
        return @YES;
    }
    if ([lowercased isEqualToString:@"false"]) {
        return @NO;
    }

    NSNumberFormatter *formatter = [[NSNumberFormatter alloc] init];
    formatter.locale = [NSLocale localeWithLocaleIdentifier:@"en_US_POSIX"];
    NSNumber *number = [formatter numberFromString:string];
    if (number) {
        return number;
    }

    return string;
}

@end
```

**为什么这版能过**
- 原始 query 先按 `&` 拆，能保住顶层参数边界。
- 每个 entry 解码后只取**第一个** `=`：
  - `data={"rich_message":... "link":"https://... ?l=zh-Hans-CN" ...}`
  - key 是 `data`
  - value 是后面整串 JSON
- 内层 URL 的 `=` 不会再把 entry 拆成 3 段。

**你这个 case 会怎么变**
- 服务器下发：
  - `webox:///action/popup?data%3D%7B...%22link%22%3A%22https%3A...%3Fl%3Dzh-Hans-CN%22...%7D`
- 经过这个新解析后：
  - `userInfo[@"data"]` 会是完整 JSON 字符串
- 然后 `/Users/liuyifu/Documents/oversea/AppHub/WhatsBox/WhatsBox/Core/Service/Routing/WBRouteActionManager.m:251`
  - `[userInfo[@"data"] jsonValueDecoded]`
